title: Logger interval changed to 5 minutes
description: On November 15, 2010, all dataloggers at Angelo Reserve were set to record measurements at 5 minute intervals. Prior to this we had the following intervals in minutes:  Weather Stations: HQ: 5 TreeBeard: 5 Angelo Meadow: 15 HQ: 15 StillingWell: 15  Rivendell: level 1_1: 60 level 1_2: 30 level 2_1: 60 level 2_2: 30 level 3_1: 60 level 3_2: 30 level 4_1: 30  Comments:undefined incident report migrated from SensorDB.
